      "audioText": "我用小猫给你解释一下，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 7.73,
      "endTime": 8.63,
      "audioText": "小猫从来不懂。"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 8.63,
      "endTime": 9.33,
      "audioText": "什么叫烦恼？"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 9.33,
      "endTime": 10.65,
      "audioText": "可社区里的其他小猫，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 10.71,
      "endTime": 11.91,
      "audioText": "日子从来都不轻松。"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 11.99,
      "endTime": 12.87,
      "audioText": "黑猫患了抑郁，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 12.95,
      "endTime": 14.01,
      "audioText": "整天耷拉着耳朵，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 14.01,
      "endTime": 14.91,
      "audioText": "趴在窝里不动。"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 14.99,
      "endTime": 16.39,
      "audioText": "小猫路过总笑着劝它，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 16.41,
      "endTime": 18.79,
      "audioText": "别总板着脸开心点蓝猫满是焦虑，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 18.79,
      "endTime": 19.51,
      "audioText": "整天魂不守，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 19.51,
      "endTime": 20.29,
      "audioText": "舍坐立不安。"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 20.31,
      "endTime": 22.81,
      "audioText": "它就说你就是想太多放宽心就没事。"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 22.93,
      "endTime": 23.95,
      "audioText": "橘猫严重社恐，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 24.03,
      "endTime": 25.39,
      "audioText": "每次聚会都躲在角落，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 25.41,
      "endTime": 26.11,
      "audioText": "浑身发抖，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 26.13,
      "endTime": 26.83,
      "audioText": "它又凑过去，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 26.83,
      "endTime": 27.79,
      "audioText": "喊你勇敢点，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 27.81,
      "endTime": 28.69,
      "audioText": "有什么好怕的，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 28.71,
      "endTime": 30.83,
      "audioText": "小猫一直不明白自己的好心安慰，"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 30.85,
      "endTime": 32.03,
      "audioText": "为什么从来没人听？"
    },
    {
      "startTime": 32.11,
